machine_end_gcode:
; Move away and park
{if max_layer_z < max_print_height}G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+1, max_print_height)} F720  ; Move print head up{endif}
G1 X125 Y0 F3600                                                                               ; park
{if max_layer_z < max_print_height}G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+20, max_print_height)} F720 ; Move print head further up{endif}

G4                                                                                           ; wait
M220 S100                                                                                    ; reset speed factor
M221 S100                                                                                    ; reset flow
M572 D0 S0.0                                                                                 ; reset pressure advance
M290 R0 S0                                                                                   ; reset babystep

M104 S0                                                                                      ; turn off temperature
M107                                                                                         ; turn off fan

; Heatbed cooling notification service
M140 S43                                                                                     ; turn off heatbed
M116 H0 S2                                                                                   ; Wait for the bed to hit 45-50C
M144                                                                                         ; Set bed to standy

; Beep twice
M300 S1500 P1500
G4 P2500
M300 S1500 P1500

; Bring the heat plate forward
G1 X0 Y210 F3600

M84                                                                                          ; disable motors
; max_layer_z = [max_layer_z]
machine_start_gcode:
G90                                 ; use absolute coordinates
M83                                 ; extruder relative mode

; Check whether printer filament matches - {filament_type[0]}
M98 P"/macros/Utility/Validate Slicer Param" F"{filament_type[0]}" B"{curr_bed_type}"

; First phase heating routine - Stabilize heating conditions for stable bed probing
M190 S{min(70, first_layer_bed_temperature[0])}                            ; heat up bed to 70C (or first layer bed temp, if lower) to have it hot enough for the probing sequence (that can keep its temp between each probe)
M109 S160                           ; heat up the nozzle first (to warm up PINDA gently & filament retraction)

; Bed probing routine
G28                                 ; Home printer
M557 X{max(25, min(85, first_layer_print_min[0] - 20))}:{min(245, max(165, first_layer_print_max[0] + 20))} Y{max(4, min(70, first_layer_print_min[1] - 20))}:{min(205, max(140, first_layer_print_max[1] + 20))} P3:3
G32                                 ; Probe bed (/sys/bed.g)

; Preparing to start print
G1 X100 Y-2 F10000                  ; Go roughly where the intro line is going to go
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; wait for bed temp

M109 S[first_layer_temperature]     ; wait for extruder temp
M582 T8                             ; double check to make sure filament is loaded

M300 S1200 P1200                    ; Beep to inform that print is starting
G4 S5                               ; Wait for 5 seconds
G1 Z0.6 F720                        ; Hover 0.6mm above bed

; Intro line
G1 E12 F1000                        ; Blob
G1 X150 E8 F1000                    ; Intro line
G92 E0
G1 Z[first_layer_height] F720
name: Prusa MK2X Duet 0.6 nozzle
